This account is used to manage the [http://sites.imagej.net/LOCI/ LOCI update site]. See also [[List of update sites]].

To activate it:

* [[Update_Sites|{{bc|Help|Update...}}]]
* Click ''Manage update sites''
* Check ''LOCI''
* Click ''Close''

Some files should appear on the list with ''Status/Action'' of ''Install it''.

* Click ''Apply changes''
* Restart ImageJ

Your ImageJ should now possess additional commands in the ''Plugins > LOCI'' menu.
